                        <h2>About</h2>
						<h3 class = "justify_text">OpenCode is the official Open Source Software Society of NIT Rourkela.The society is run by a bunch of coding enthusiats with a sole motive to create and maintain the deployement as well as to enhance its level. We also welcome student/professor initiated open source software/hardware projects. The society aims to educate the interested student fraternity about real world collaborative software development and Open Source tools which can enable them to come up with their own unique and out-of-the box ideas. Our objective is to accomplish this by organising workshops and seminars by experienced open source developers, instructors, and enthusiasts. </h3>
